<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Developer Portfolio | Professional Showcase</title>
    <style>
        /* Modern Design Tokens & Variables */
        :root {
            --bg-main: #0d1117;
            --bg-card: #161b22;
            --border-color: #30363d;
            --text-primary: #c9d1d9;
            --text-secondary: #8b949e;
            --accent: #58a6ff;
            --accent-success: #238636;
            --font-stack: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Reset & Global Styles */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-main);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: var(--font-stack);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Header Component */
        header {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .profile-title h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .profile-title p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }

        .status-badge {
            background-color: rgba(56, 139, 253, 0.1);
            color: var(--accent);
            border: 1px solid rgba(56, 139, 253, 0.4);
            padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 2em;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Section Layouts */
        section {
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Grid Component for Projects */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        /* Repository / Project Card Module */
        .card {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .card-title {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .card-title:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .card-desc {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            height: 40px;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .lang-dot {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-right: 0.25rem;
        }

        .dot-html { background-color: #e34c26; }
        .dot-js { background-color: #f1e05a; }
        .dot-py { background-color: #3572a5; }

        /* Contribution Metric / Tech Stack Layout */
        .tech-stack {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .tech-tag {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        /* Action Footer */
        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="profile-title">
                <h1>Engineering Showcase</h1>
                <p>Building high-performance, accessible web architectures.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="status-badge">🟢 Open for Collaborations</span>
        </header>

        <section>
            <h2>Architectural Focus</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; max-width: 750px;">
                Specializing in semantic markup systems, modular design tokens, and optimal client-side execution. Focused on parsing high-density interfaces down into clean, performant modules.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Pinned Repositories</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <a href="#" class="card-title">core-markup-engine</a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-desc">A highly-optimized structural layout boiler engine tailored for lightning-fast DOM parsing and structural indexing.</p>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span><span class="lang-dot dot-html"></span>HTML5</span>
                        <span>⭐ 142</span>
                        <span>Updated recently</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <a href="#" class="card-title">async-data-hydrator</a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-desc">Asynchronous document tree structure formatting engine designed for rapid rendering and state hydration.</p>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span><span class="lang-dot dot-js"></span>JavaScript</span>
                        <span>⭐ 98</span>
                        <span>Updated 2 days ago</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <a href="#" class="card-title">document-to-pdf-compiler</a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-desc">Server-side automated layout pipeline compiling direct client images and structured trees directly into print-ready artifacts.</p>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span><span class="lang-dot dot-py"></span>Python</span>
                        <span>⭐ 314</span>
                        <span>Updated 1 week ago</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Environment & Toolkit</h2>
            <div class="tech-stack">
                <span class="tech-tag">HTML5 (Semantic)</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">CSS3 (Grid/Variables)</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">ES6+ JavaScript</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Git / Workflow Automation</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Python Pipeline Automation</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Git-Showcase Layout Engine. Built cleanly with standard native web APIs.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
